ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3017\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3017-TW</a>)、健策 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3653:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3653\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3653-TW</a>)</strong></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><strong>PCB：金像電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2383:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2383\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2383-TW</a>)、定穎 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3715:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3715\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3715-TW</a>)、博智 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8155:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8155\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8155-TW</a>)、欣興 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3037:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3037\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3037-TW</a>)、南電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8046:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8046\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8046-TW</a>)、台光電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2383:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2383\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2383-TW</a>)</strong></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><strong>CPO：上詮 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3363:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3363\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3363-TW</a>)、波若威 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3163:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3163\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3163-TW</a>)、眾達 - KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4977:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4977\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4977-TW</a>)、環宇 - KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4991:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4991\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4991-TW</a>)、IET-KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4971:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4971\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4971-TW</a>)</strong></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><strong>個股詳細解析：</strong></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><strong>創意 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3443:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3443\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3443-TW</a>)：ASIC 與矽智財 IP。隨 AI 晶片需求爆發，客製化 AI 晶片設計服務需求強勁。</strong></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><strong>穎崴 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6515:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6515\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6515-TW</a>)：全球前三大  Test Socket</strong> <strong>供應商，</strong><strong> CPO </strong><strong>先進封裝領域布局領先</strong><strong>。</strong></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><strong>旺矽 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6223:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6223\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6223-TW</a>)：全球頂尖探針卡廠，VPC 在高階測試領域市佔率高，台積電 CoWoS 擴產帶動的測試介面需求。</strong></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><strong>台達電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2308:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2308\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2308-TW</a>)： AI 伺服器電源與 液冷散熱元件 出貨強勁。800V DC 高壓直流供電方案。</strong></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><strong>貿聯 - KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3665:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3665\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3665-TW</a>)：具有機櫃層級的電力連接與高速資料互連技術，轉型為「系統級互連解決方案提供者」。</strong></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><strong>定穎 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3715:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3715\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3715-TW</a>)：輝達 Rubin 平台、高階 GPU 及 Switch 主機板供應鏈。AI ASIC 加速器卡已通過認證。</strong></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><strong>金像電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2383:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2383\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2383-TW</a>)：ASIC 主板與交換器，為美系主流 ASIC 平台主要供應商。</strong></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><strong>環宇 - KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4991:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4991\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4991-TW</a>)：4 吋 InP 晶圓廠產能。主要客戶包含： Innolight、Lumentum 及 Coherent。</strong></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><strong>眾達 - KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4977:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4977\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4977-TW</a>)：博通在 CPO 領域的核心夥伴。51.2T TH5-Bailey CPO 產品進入量產。</strong></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><strong>本週市場大幅修正後，許多 AI 績優股回測十日或月均線支撐，已經回到相對低檔區位置，過去被軋空手的投資朋友，現在又有新機會，錯過還是掌握？現在就是關鍵的時候，更多的選股資訊，歡迎加入 Line @</strong></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><strong>更多產業趨勢預告 + 盤中訊息→<br/>\n都在葉老師的 Line @：<br/>\nLINE@ID：@money668 (@要記得加)</strong></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><a href=\"https://user225916.pse.is/money668\"><strong>https://user225916.pse.is/money668</strong></a></p></section><section style=\"margin-